					For more information about how ENGYS has leveraged Pointwise meshing to enable topology optimization of automotive components, watch Dr. Combest’s presentation entitled &ldquo;<a href="https://info.pointwise.com/topology-optimization-pointwise-helyx-adjoint">Topology Optimization with Pointwise and HELYX Adjoint</a>.&rdquo;
